data.description: Your new Florida home is now on the market. Live the Florida lifestyle.  Immediate Occupancy. This Hamsher Homes Three bedroom Two bath Pool home on saltwater access canal is awaiting a new family to call it home. The Living room overlooks pool and lanai area through sliding glass doors. Separate  dining room for family gatherings or use the bar seating in kitchen for casual dining. Kitchen is open to family room so conversations can continue while preparing snacks or meals for guest and family. Large master suite with two walk-in closets has en-suite bath and French Doors to the lanai and pool area. Master bath is equipped with dual sinks, separate shower and garden soaking tub. Split floorplan give you privacy for guest in second and third bedrooms.  Large inside laundry/utility room has space for additional shelving for storage. New Roof in 2023 and a/c in 2017. Waterfront has concrete seawall with composite dock and 10,000# boat lift. Quiet neighborhood with easy access to shopping and the amenities of the easy Florida living.
